      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "CUSTODY (1) has missed the placings at his last couple but was in the money three back when second (23.97) at this track in a Mix 5. Can make amends this time. VERACIOUS VAL (8) broke a string of placings finishing in the money two on end before a last start fourth (31.42) at Q Lakeside. Has a good record at this journey. Yet to miss the placings from seven starts out of this box. Key player if finds best. ZIPPING OLSEN (2) returned a better run last time, finishing in the money (24.27) at this track behind Quest For Pace in a Mix 5. Has the early speed to land on the pace and can stick on. Some good form is emerging from her last run. Expected to feature again. CANE SMOKE (3) with some luck can improve on an unplaced run last time here.",
